me-weighted average premium between perpetual and spot prices. Long positions pay negative funding rates when the perpetual trades below spot, while short positions pay when above spot. OKX's portfolio margin mode allows cross-collateralization with other positions, reducing margin requirements for funding rate strategies."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
